 Timi Dakolo and Wife, Bukola Dakolo stepped out with friends today with no indication of tension in their appearance. This is Bukola’s first photo to surface on the internet after her explosive interview that implicated COZA pastor, Biodun Fatoyinbo in a rape allegation. There were reports that Busola had been traumatised and crying endlessly since the interview. But it seems she’s doing just fine in these new photos as she hung out with her friends Waje, Bovi, Debola Williams, Latasha Ngwube today Sunday July 7th.  The post Busola Dakolo Posts First Photos Of Herself, Weeks After Her Explosive Interview appeared first on . Source: 36Ng